reviewText: Dennis Swanburg is just great!! He is clean, family friendly, and most importantly, Christ-centered! He will have you laughing so hard, you'll be in tears & your sides will hurt!
Another good one for Dennis Swanberg. He is a funny guy and always makes your troubles seem less important than they did before you watch it.

Dennis Swanberg is the greatest.  Clean, good comedy that has you
laughing the whole time.....you can relate many times with his stories
of childhood....wonderful video.
